<h2>Sample Volume Tab Plugin</h2>

<p>This sample tab is rendered by a custom <code>VolumeTabProvider</code>.</p>

{{#if name}}
<div>
  <p><strong>Volume:</strong> {{name}}</p>
  <p><strong>ID:</strong> {{id}}</p>
	<p><strong>Description:</strong> {{description}}</p>
	<p><strong>Display Name:</strong> {{deviceDisplayName}}</p>
</div>
{{else}}
<p>No volume details were provided to the renderer.</p>
{{/if}}

<p>Use this sample as a starting point for displaying capacity, replication, performance, or storage-system metadata.</p>

